snippet.textDisplay:
You know, I actually had my foot pierced by a hair strand one time.
It was long ago and I had completely forgotten about it...


Anyway, I stepped into said hair strand and for some reason it pierced my foot from below.
Think stepping into a needle, but just with a hair strand instead.


Had this stinging pain in my right foot every time I took a step and it took me a while to realize something's off and check my foot.
And I saw this large hair strand sticking out of my foot's underside.
Took a bit of effort to pull it out and it actually bled a tiny bit, after getting it out.


But the pain stopped and I went on with my day.
So that's my little story of getting pierced by a hair strand. : 3
